<div class="post-bodycopy clearfix"></p>
<p>The Sita Sings the Blues trailer is up for a Freddie Award in the &#8220;Best Design&#8221; category. It&#8217;s one of those &#8220;viewer-votes&#8221; things &#8211; aka &#8220;get the filmmakers to do the publicity and spam everyone they know to go to your site and increase its ratings for advertisers and investors&#8221; things &#8211; so if you have the time and inclination and don&#8217;t mind being used as a pawn please go here and vote for it.</p>
<p>(Unrelated to the Freddie award, there&#8217;s a newer version of the Sita trailer featuring the soon-to-be-infamous &#8220;shadow puppets&#8221; on the Tribeca site (click the &#8220;trailers&#8221; tab). )</p>
